'''Clare''' was one of the mourners at Pete's funeral party.

==History==
At Pete's funeral, Clare told Violet about Pete using acupuncture to help her cope with the side effects of her chemotherapy. When she started crying while talking, Violet told her that Pete wanted a celebration.
